---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section id="about" eyebrow="about" title="A short version">
  <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-ink)]/90">
    <p>
      Originally from Romania. I moved to Amsterdam a few years ago for
      university and a change of scenery.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of coursework, most of my free time goes into prototyping pieces
      of video games — characters, menus, small systems — as a way to learn
      new techniques and tools.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not building, I read fiction and watch films. Both feed a
      lasting interest in narration, character development, and dialogue, which
      I'd like to carry into the games I work on.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
